data.description: Discover your breathtaking waterfront haven in Mosaic! Built in 2018, this exquisite property features 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, and an additional flex space, setting the stage for opulent living. As you approach, the sophisticated paver driveway and inviting exterior draw you in. Inside, a plethora of premium features await, including an advanced lighting system, decorative tray ceilings, and a mix of elegant tile and plush carpeting throughout. The kitchen is a chef's dream, outfitted with tall 42-inch cabinetry, a chic tile backsplash, high-end stainless steel appliances, and luxurious granite counters. The home is also equipped with a large walk-in pantry, an energy-efficient water heating system, an immersive surround sound setup, and a comprehensive central vacuuming system. The ... master suite is a sanctuary of relaxation, offering a lavish Roman bathtub and an expansive walk-in wardrobe. Each bedroom offers ample space, enhancing the home's allure with a high-tech security and WiFi setup for ultimate comfort. Outside, the community amenities, including dual swimming pools, a modern fitness center, a children's play area, a scenic lakefront promenade, and cozy firepits, add to the lifestyle. Located conveniently close to shopping centers, dining options, and entertainment venues, this property is a rare find. Seize the opportunity to make this dream house your own - contact us now for more details! equipped with brand new assumable solar power with monthly lease of $247.29/month
